	(247,86,'product_description','The $20 Premium U Card has up to 23 local discounts, national discounts after registration, two keytags and 6 national coupons.\r\n\r\nOur cards offer tremendous savings for the customer, which allows the seller to be successful, which in turns leads to a great fundraiser.\r\n\r\nSelling Season: July-August\r\nTime Frame Needed to Begin: 6 weeks'),
