	(281,104,'member_email',''),
	(282,104,'memberprofile','<p>I\'m in my third year working in the fundraising business and I\'m very excited to work with athletes and coaches. I would say I\'m no stranger to athletics, having been around the game of football for most of my life.</p>\r\n<p>I played high school football for Millard West before going to the University of Nebraska Omaha. While at UNO I earned a degree in Business Management. After playing at UNO, I had the opportunity to try out for the Detroit Lions. I now look forward to using my leadership and communication skills off the field with coaches and students in the fundraising business.</p>'),
