	(301,106,'member_email',''),
	(302,106,'memberprofile','<p>Hi, my name is Jeff Kerr. I have been a teacher, coach, and fundraising consultant for the past twenty five years. This experience has helped me understand how important it is for coaches to earn the most amount of money with the least amount of effort. </p>\r\n<p>I am currently a sales trainer and coach for Fundraising University. My responsibility is to help Fundraising University stay on the cutting edge of fundraising and develop our value based program so every coach has a successful experience and maximizes their financial goals. I am also a personal development coach. I mentor, empower, and motivate individuals to achieve balance and help them discover their passion and purpose in life. I live in Omaha, Nebraska with my wife Sandy.</p>\r\n<p>Our hobbies include spending time with our children, traveling the country on our Harley, and enjoying time with friends.</p>'),
