	(367,122,'testimonial_title','Aaron Holst - Excelsior Springs High School'),
	(368,122,'testimonialletter','<p>Working with Fundraising University has been the best move I’ve made as a coach when it comes to raising funds for our baseball and softball programs. Their program provides great products for our athletes to sell, and their staff educates our athletes on how to sell the products better. Additionally, every member of their staff has background as former athletes. They know what incentives motivated them as former players, and they share that insight to help motivate our athletes to strive for better things for our program. A relationship with Fundraising University is a no-brainer!</p>'),
	(369,122,'testimonialsignature','<p>Aaron Holst<br />Head Baseball/Softball<br />Excelsior Springs High School</p>'),
