	(391,125,'testimonial_title','Coach Kurt Frenzen - Columbus Lakeview High School'),
	(392,125,'testimonialletter','<p>We have been a loyal customer with Fundraising University for the past 6 years. They will remain our source for fundraising for years and years to come. They are friendly and professional to our coaches, players, and customers. They also have a great relationship with the companies that support us through the sponsoring of our cards. They go above and beyond any fundraising company that I have ever dealt with to make sure that we have all the support and means necessary to reach our goal each and every year. Fundraising University was not the first company that we used, but they will definitely be the last.</p>'),
