	(709,212,'product_name','Ticket'),
	(710,212,'product_description','Our ticket package is another great discount product that delivers incredible results. This product is comprised of 40 local vendor coupons that range from anywhere from $3 per coupon to $10 per coupon in value. At the very minimum, that’s over $120 in savings!\r\n\r\nThe ticket also allows access to over 60,000 local national discounts as well.\r\n\r\nSelling Season: February-June\r\nTime Frame Needed to Begin: 4 weeks'),
