	(12,1,'2012-01-05 07:03:28','2012-01-05 07:03:28','<p>All of our discount products are personalized to the individual school or group that is doing the fundraising, and we take care of all the upfront costs in printing and designing the products ourselves. In addition, Fundraising University will contact local merchants in your area so we can provide the best discount options for your fundraiser from both local and national companies.</p>\r\n<p>Profit margins are determined by how well the sale goes, and increases with more sales.</p>\r\n','Fundraising Options','','publish','open','open','','fundraising-options','','','2012-01-22 04:40:34','2012-01-22 04:40:34','',0,'http://localhost/fundraisingu/?page_id=12',3,'page','',0),
