	(35,1,'2012-01-21 22:29:50','2012-01-21 22:29:50','<p><strong>Fundraising University</strong> was established in the spring of 2009. Our team consists of former high school and college athletes along with former youth, high school and college coaches.</p>\n<p>With over ten years of fundraising experience, we have found that there is a right way and a wrong way to execute a fundraiser. Our formula combines using the<strong> right product with the right group during the right time of the year</strong> to ensure the greatest amount of profit for each team we work with.</p>\n<p>Our goal is to help coaches and sponsors raise as much money as they can in a short amount of time. As former coaches and athletes, we understand that fundraising isn\'t always the most enjoyable part of a coach\'s or athlete\'s season. Because of this, we personally visit each school group to teach the coach and students how to raise as much money for their program as they can in a short amount of time, so they can get back to doing what they are there to do - coach and play.</p>\n<p><strong>P.O. Box 540314</strong><br /><strong>Omaha, NE 68154</strong><br /><strong>1.800.217.1962 (main)</strong><br /><strong> 1.800.854.7699 (fax)</strong></p>','About','','inherit','closed','open','','10-autosave','','','2012-01-21 22:29:50','2012-01-21 22:29:50','',10,'http://localhost/fundraisingu/2012/10-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),
