	(238,1,'2012-01-18 22:29:24','2012-01-18 22:29:24','<p>Fundraising University was established in the spring of 2009. Our team consists of former high school and college athletes along with former youth, high school and college coaches.</p>\r\n<p>With over ten years of fundraising experience, we have found that there is a right way and a wrong way to execute a fundraiser. Our formula combines using the right product with the right group during the right time of the year to ensure the greatest amount of profit for each team we work with.</p>\r\n<p>Our goal is to help coaches and sponsors raise as much money as they can in a short amount of time. As former coaches and athletes, we understand that fundraising isn\'t always the most enjoyable part of a coach\'s or athlete\'s season. Because of this, we personally visit each school group to teach the coach and students how to raise as much money for their program as they can in a short amount of time, so they can get back to doing what they are there to do - coach and play.</p>\r\n<p>P.O. Box 540314<br /> Omaha, NE 68154<br /> 1.800.217.1962 (main)<br /> 1.800.854.7699 (fax)</p>','About','','inherit','closed','open','','10-revision-29','','','2012-01-18 22:29:24','2012-01-18 22:29:24','',10,'http://the-17.local/fundraisingu/2012/10-revision-29/',0,'revision','',0),
